a-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fashleys-lgbct-moment-viral-ahead-of-tonights-massive-biden-vs-trump%2Famp_articleshow%2F111317131.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fashleys-lgbct-moment-viral-ahead-of-tonights-massive-biden-vs-trump%2Famp_articleshow%2F111317131.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20%26quot%3BSecret%20Meeting%26quot%3B%20Quip%20On%20Lift%20Encounter%20With%20D%20Fadnavis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20accidental%20meeting%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20Maharashtra%20Assembly's%20monsoon%20session%2C%20arch-rivals%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20found%20themselves%20waiting%20for%20the%20lift%20together.%20Awkwardness%20was%20in%20the%20air%2C%20and%20a%20video%20that%20has%20now%20gone%20viral%20shows%20the%20two%20former%20Chief%20Ministers%20exchanging%20some%20words%3B%20the%20mood%20is%20cold%20at%20best.%20While%20what%20they%20spoke%20about%20is%20not%20known%2C%20the%20body%20language%20suggests%20that%20it%20was%20little%20more%20than%20small%20talk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thackeray%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20conversation%20when%20he%20interacted%20with%20the%20media%20later.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20here%20on%2C%20we%20will%20do%20all%20our%20secret%20meetings%20in%20the%20lift%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20joked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Devendraji%20and%20I%20were%20in%20the%20lift%2C%20people%20must%20have%20thought%20of%20the%20song%2C%20'na%20na%20karte%20pyar%20tumhi%20se%20kar%20baithe'%20(a%20classic%20from%20the%201965%20film%20Jab%20Jab%20Phool%20Khile%20that%20roughly%20translates%20to%20'I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20you%20despite%20denials).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20nothing%20like%20that.%20It%20was%20an%20unexpected%20meeting%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20chief%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20gave%20the%20incident%20a%20different%20spin.%20%26quot%3BTwo%20years%20ago%2C%20they%20(Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20his%20team)%20took%20a%20different%20lift%20and%20went%20to%20the%20Congress.%20We%20took%20one%20that%20carried%20us%20to%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20light-hearted%20interaction%2C%20pictures%20of%20which%20have%20emerged%2C%20was%20between%20BJP%20minister%20Chandrakant%20Patil%20and%20Mr%20Thackeray.%20When%20the%20BJP%20leader%20gave%20a%20bar%20of%20chocolate%20to%20Mr%20Thackeray%2C%20he%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BTomorrow%20you%20will%20give%20chocolate%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Maharashtra.%26quot%3B%20The%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20was%20clearly%20referring%20to%20the%20state%20budget%20that%20is%20likely%20to%20offer%20sops%20to%20woo%20voters%20ahead%20of%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20last%20Assembly%20session%20before%20the%20Maharashtra%20election%20due%20later%20this%20year.%20These%20polls%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20tight%20contest%20after%20the%20MVA%20trumped%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20of%20BJP%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Eknath%20Shinde)%20and%20NCP%20(Ajit%20Pawar)%20in%20this%20general%20election.%20Out%20of%20the%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20the%20MVA%20won%2030%20and%20the%20NDA%20bloc%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20upcoming%20election%20is%20significant%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20splits%20in%20two%20key%20political%20forces%20in%20the%20state%20over%20the%20past%20two%20years.%20In%20the%20last%20state%20election%20in%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20undivided%20Shiv%20Sena%20fought%20in%20alliance%20and%20secured%20a%20majority.%20But%20the%20allies%20fell%20out%20over%20rotational%20chiefministership%20and%20Mr%20Thackeray%20tied%20up%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20to%20form%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20however%2C%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20government%20was%20toppled%20after%20his%20trusted%20lieutenant%20Eknath%20Shinde%20led%20a%20mutiny%20that%20split%20the%20Shiv%20Sena.%20Mr%20Shinde%20tied%20up%20with%20the%20BJP%20to%20form%20the%20next%20government.%20Subsequently%2C%20NCP%20leader%20Ajit%20Pawar%20rebelled%20against%20his%20uncle%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20split%20in%20NCP.%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20too%2C%20joined%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719490740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F7camhtto_uddhav-fadnavis-lift_625x300_27_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fuddhav-thackeray-devendra-fadnavis-uddhav-thackerays-secret-meeting-quip-on-lift-encounter-with-d-fadnavis-5981292%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20accidental%20meeting%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20Maharashtra%20Assembly's%20monsoon%20session%2C%20arch-rivals%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20found%20themselves%20waiting%20for%20the%20lift%20together.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fuddhav-thackeray-devendra-fadnavis-uddhav-thackerays-secret-meeting-quip-on-lift-encounter-with-d-fadnavis-5981292%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fuddhav-thackeray-devendra-fadnavis-uddhav-thackerays-secret-meeting-quip-on-lift-encounter-with-d-fadnavis-5981292%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fuddhav-thackeray-devendra-fadnavis-uddhav-thackerays-secret-meeting-quip-on-lift-encounter-with-d-fadnavis-5981292%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bolivia's%20failed%20coup%20attempt...%20in%2075%20seconds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719490739000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F8c9c%2Flive%2F5f082e30-347e-11ef-bdc5-41d7421c2adf.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc2e4pv9zdmpo%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20all%20started%20when%20the%20presidential%20palace%20in%20La%20Paz%20was%20stormed%20by%20soldiers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc2e4pv9zdmpo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Salman-Jacqueline%20starrer%20'Kick%202'%20delayed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719490687000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111317100%2Cimgsize-27616.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsalman-khan-and-jacqueline-fernandez-starrer-kick-2-delayed-for-this-reason%2Farticleshow%2F111317100.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111317100.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EActor%20Salman%20Khan%20who%20is%20gearing%20up%20for%20his%20upcoming%20film%2C%20'Sikandar'%2C%20is%20set%20to%20mark%20his%20reunion%20with%20producer%20Sajid%20Nadiadwala%20after%20their%202014%20hit%2C%20'Kick'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsalman-khan-and-jacqueline-fernandez-starrer-kick-2-delayed-for-this-reason%2Farticleshow%2F111317100.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPride%20Of%20Every%20Tamilian%26quot%3B%3A%20Minister%20Attacks%20Opposition%20Over%20'Sengol'%20Demand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition's%20push%20to%20keep%20the%20Constitution%20front%20and%20centre%20by%20asking%20for%20the%20'sengol'%2C%20a%20sceptre%20kept%20next%20to%20the%20Speaker's%20chair%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20to%20be%20replaced%20by%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20text%20has%20led%20to%20a%20strong%20pushback%20by%20the%20government%2C%20which%20has%20accused%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20of%20disrespecting%20the%20baton%20and%20what%20it%20symbolises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MP%20RK%20Chaudhary%20writing%20to%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20and%20asking%20for%20the%20'sengol'%20to%20be%20replaced%20by%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20junior%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20L%20Murugan%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20sceptre%20is%20the%20pride%20of%20every%20Tamilian.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20also%20mentioned%20in%20Tirukkural%20(a%20classic%20Tamil%20text%20by%20poet%20and%20philosopher%20Thiruvalluvar)%2C%20which%20spoke%20about%20how%20the%20sengol%20plays%20a%20role%20in%20government.%20When%20India%20got%20freedom%2C%20(Governor%20General)%20Mountbatten%20and%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20had%20spoken%20about%20how%20power%20would%20be%20handed%20over%20after%20Independence%20and%20when%20Rajaji%20(C%20Rajagopalachari)%20was%20consulted%2C%20he%20said%20it%20can%20be%20done%20using%20a%20sengol%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Murugan%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20former%20president%20of%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20BJP%2C%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five-foot-long%20sceptre%2C%20made%20of%20gold%2C%20was%20commissioned%20by%20the%20Thiruvavaduthurai%20Adheenam%20(math%20pontiff)%20and%20sent%20to%20Delhi.%20The%20minister%20said%20that%20the%20'sengol'%20was%20given%20to%20%C2%A0Nehru%20after%20conducting%20rituals%20but%20it%20%26quot%3Bwas%20not%20valued%26quot%3B%20and%20sent%20somewhere.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%2C%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20found%20out%20where%20the%20'sengol'%20was%20kept%20(Allahabad%20Museum)%20and%20brought%20it%20to%20the%20new%20Parliament%20building.%20It%20was%20installed%20in%20the%20new%20Parliament%20after%20rituals%20were%20conducted%20by%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Adheenams.%20The%20sengol%20symbolises%20a%20fair%20government.%20The%20INDIA%20alliance%20does%20not%20value%20the%20sengol.%20Its%20attitude%20is%20condemnable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Mr%20Chaudhary%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20MP%20from%20Mohanlalganj%2C%20had%20sparked%20a%20row%20by%20asking%20for%20the%20'sengol'%20to%20be%20replaced%20to%20%26quot%3Bsave%20democracy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20adoption%20of%20the%20Constitution%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20democracy%20in%20the%20country%2C%20and%20the%20Constitution%20is%20its%20symbol.%20The%20BJP%20government%20in%20its%20last%20term%20installed%20'sengol'%20next%20to%20the%20Speaker's%20chair.%20Sengol%20is%20a%20Tamil%20word%20that%20means%20sceptre.%20Rajdand%20also%20means%20the%20king's%20stick.%20We%20have%20become%20independent%20after%20the%20age%20of%20kings.%20Now%2C%20every%20man%20and%20woman%20who%20is%20an%20eligible%20voter%20chooses%20the%20government%20to%20run%20this%20country.%20So%20will%20the%20country%20run%20by%20Constitution%20or%20by%20a%20king's%20stick%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20SP%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20demand%20was%20backed%20by%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20and%20MP%20B%20Manickam%20Tagore%2C%20an%20MP%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20who%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20very%20clear%20that%20the%20'sengol'%20symbolises%20kingship%20and%20the%20kingdom-era%20is%20over.%20We%20should%20celebrate%20the%20people's%20democracy%20and%20the%20Constitution.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20said%20the%20demand%20reflects%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%20%26quot%3Bhatred%26quot%3B%20for%20Tamil%20culture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSamajwadi%20Party%20has%20no%20respect%20for%20Indian%20history%20or%20culture.%20The%20remarks%20of%20their%20top%20leaders%20on%20the%20Sengol%20are%20condemnable%20and%20indicate%20their%20ignorance.%20It%20also%20shows%20INDI%20Alliance's%20hatred%20to%20Tamil%20culture%20in%20particular%20The%20Sengol%20is%20India's%20pride%20and%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20honour%20that%20Hon.%20PM%20Shri%20%40narendramodi%20Ji%20accorded%20it%20the%20highest%20respect%20in%20the%20Parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'sengol'%20was%20installed%20in%20the%20new%20Parliament%20on%20May%2028%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719490500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fnsf1uo3_l-murugan_625x300_27_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpride-of-every-tamilian-minister-attacks-opposition-over-sengol-demand-5982498%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20opposition's%20push%20to%20keep%20the%20Constitution%20front%20and%20centre%20by%20asking%20for%20the%20'sengol'%2C%20a%20sceptre%20kept%20next%20to%20the%20Speaker's%20chair%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20to%20be%20replaced%20by%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20text%20has%20led%20to%20a%20strong%20pushback%20by%20the%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpride-of-every-tamilian-minister-attacks-opposition-over-sengol-demand-5982498%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpride-of-every-tamilian-minister-attacks-opposition-over-sengol-demand-5982498%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpride-of-every-tamilian-minister-attacks-opposition-over-sengol-demand-5982498%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Les%20Films%20du%20Losange%20Takes%20Sales%20on%20Mafia%20Drama%20%E2%80%98Sicilian%20Letters%E2%80%99%20as%20First-Look%20Images%20of%20Elio%20Germano%20and%20Toni%20Servillo%20Are%20Revealed%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719490381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FElio-Germano.jpg%3Fw%