_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indianapolis%20is%20the%20US%20city%20with%20the%20highest%20birth%20rate%2C%20study%20finds%2C%20which%20could%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20its%20future%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222959%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Skyline%20of%20Indianapolis%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667d30bbd1c84a0eaca82bb4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221945%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAccording%20to%20a%20new%20study%2C%20Indianapolis%20has%20the%20highest%20birth%20rate%20out%20of%2037%20of%20the%20US's%20largest%20cities.%3Cp%3EDavel5957%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIndianapolis%20has%20the%20highest%20birth%20rate%20among%20major%20US%20cities%2C%20per%20SmartAsset%20analysis.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20used%20US%20Census%20data%20from%202021-2022%20to%20compare%20birth%20rates%20in%2037%20large%20cities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EImmigration%20and%20a%20population's%20age%20composition%20could%20play%20a%20role%2C%20a%20demography%20expert%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-indiana-from-los-angeles-cheaper-housing-outdoors-tech-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndianapolis%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20US%20city%20with%20the%20highest%20birth%20rate%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fdata-studies%2Fwhere-people-have-more-children-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20analysis%20by%20the%20financial%20technology%20company%20SmartAsset.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmartAsset%20analyzed%20the%20most%20recently%20available%20US%20Census%20data%20for%2037%20of%20the%20largest%20US%20cities%20to%20determine%20where%20birth%20rates%20and%20family%20sizes%20are%20the%20highest%20and%20lowest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20looked%20at%20the%20number%20of%20women%20aged%2015%20to%2050%20who%20had%20a%20baby%20in%20the%2012%20months%20bet