s%20limitation%20in%20not%20controlling%20for%20age%20makes%20it%20challenging%20to%20distinguish%20between%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthrowing-money-schemes-wont-solve-global-fertility-crisis-demography-experts-2024-6%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBy%25202100%252C%252097%2525%2520of%2520countries%2Creverse%2520population%2520decline%252C%2520they%2520said.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efertility%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20population's%20age%20composition%2C%20and%20that%20a%20more%20precise%20measure%20would%20be%20the%20total%20fertility%20rate%2C%20which%20estimates%20the%20number%20of%20children%20a%20woman%20is%20expected%20to%20have%20over%20her%20lifetime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20most%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.in.gov%2Fhealth%2Freports%2Fnatality%2F2017%2Ftbl31_t.htm%26source%3Dgmail-imap%26ust%3D1720021046000000%26usg%3DAOvVaw3z7xKjx1fYI_KQo1Ar5u-0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndiana%20natality%20report%2C%20from%202017%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Marion%20County%2C%20which%20includes%20Indianapolis%2C%20had%20a%20total%20fertility%20rate%20of%201.933%2C%20higher%20than%20the%20overall%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fus%2Fnews%2F2024%2F04%2F27%2Fus-birth-rate-falls-to-record-low-amid-global-decline%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20rate%20of%201.62.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20demographers%20and%20governments%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fasia-countries-worry-fertility-rate-affect-armies-few-soldiers-experts-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econcerned%20about%20declining%20fertility%20rates%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20US%20and%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDudley%20L.%20Poston%20Jr.%2C%20an%20emeritus%20professor%20of%20sociology%20at%20Texas%20A%26amp%3BM%20University%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20various%20factors%20influence%20fertility%20levels%2C%20including%20e