ll-established%20in%20the%20United%20States%20at%20this%20point%2C%20it's%20still%20evolving%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20rideshares%2C%20and%20many%20riders%20may%20not%20understand%20the%20financial%20realities%20of%20rideshare%20driving%2C%26quot%3B%20Nick%20Leighton%2C%20an%20etiquette%20expert%20and%20co-host%20of%20the%20podcast%20Were%20You%20Raised%20By%20Wolves%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20via%20email.%26quot%3BThis%20may%20explain%20why%20there's%20so%20much%20inconsistency%20currently%20in%20when%20or%20how%20much%20riders%20choose%20to%20tip.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fis-driving-for-uber-worth-it-earning-strategies-gig-economy-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERide-hailing%20drivers%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20customer%20tips%20are%20hard%20to%20come%20by.%20An%20analysis%20of%20over%20500%2C000%20US%20gig%20drivers%20provided%20to%20BI%20by%20Gridwise%2C%20a%20data-analytics%20company%20that%20helps%20drivers%20track%20their%20earnings%2C%20found%20that%2028%25%20of%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20trips%20got%20tips%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20this%20year%2C%20compared%20to%20over%2070%25%20of%20food-delivery%20and%20grocery%20trips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20some%20drivers%20have%20fared%20better%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20securing%20customer%20tips.%20In%20the%20second%20half%20of%202023%2C%20Lyft%20said%20the%20median%20US%20driver%20earned%20about%20%2431%20per%20hour%20of%20engaged%20time%20%E2%80%94%20en%20route%20to%20pick%20up%20a%20passenger%20or%20had%20one%20in%20their%20vehicle.%20The%20company%20said%20these%20earnings%20included%20a%20median%20tip%20of%20%242.41%20per%20engaged%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20an%20Uber%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20in%20May%20that%20across%20the%20US%2C%20drivers%20are%20%26quot%3Bearning%20more%20than%20%2430%20an%20hour%20while%20engaged%20on%20the%20app.%26quot%3B%20Uber%20said%20that%20over%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20ride-hailing%20tipping%20frequency%20and%20the%20average%20tip%20size%20have%20roughly%20doubled%20%E2%80%94%20adding%20that%20the%20average%20ride-hailing%20tip%20amount%20rose%20nearly%2010%25%20over%20the%20past%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENine%20ride-hailing%20drivers%20shared%20what%20strategies%20have%20helped%20them%20land%20tips%20and%20why%20sometimes%20providing%20good%20service%20is%20not%20worth%20the%20effort.%20Some%20drivers%20requested%20partial%20anonymity%20due%20to%20fear%20of%20professional%20repercussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229e414f39-377e-4249-9ee7-053f177c0cc1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20drivers%20try%20to%20maximize%20tips%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStuart%20R.%2C%2055%2C%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-lyft-driver-single-mom-bus-driver-ohio-stock-walkout2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estopped%20driving%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Uber%20and%20Lyft.%20He%20reluctantly%20returned%20to%20work%20in%20IT%2C%20as%20he%20struggled%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20driving%20full-time.%20Still%2C%20he%20said%20tips%20helped%20him%20stay%20afloat%20after%20burning%20out%20from%20his%20previous%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20maintained%20a%204.99%20driver%20rating%20in%20Austin%20and%20said%20he%20frequently%20got%20tips%20for%20simple%20things%20such%20as%20greeting%20passengers%2C%20assisting%20with%20luggage%2C%20and%20keeping%20his%20car%20%26quot%3Bimmaculately%26quot%3B%20clean.%20He%20found%20he%20got%20better%20tips%20when%20he%20practiced%20%26quot%3Bsafe%20humor%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20joking%20with%20passengers%20without%20mentioning%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20he%20had%20signage%20hanging%20from%20headrests%20noting%20that%20tips%20were%20greatly%20appreciated.%20Still%2C%20he%20said%2C%20even%20keeping%20cool%20water%20on%20hot%20days%20or%20engaging%20in%20deep%20conversations%20with%20passengers%20was%20never%20a%20guarantee%20of%20a%20tip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20helpful%20to%20tourists%20has%20been%20an%20effective%20strategy%20for%20Marilyn%20Cassady%2C%20a%20five-star%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-spring-break-lyft-uber-drivers-earnings-tips-money-miami-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUber%20and%20Lyft%20driver%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Myrtle%20Beach%2C%20South%20Carolina%2C%20who%20drives%20a%20few%20days%20a%20week%20to%20supplement%20her%20Social%20Security%20income.%20She%20said%20she%20gets%20tips%20for%20nearly%2050%25%20of%20her%20rides.%20Cassady%20said%20female%20passengers%20are%20often%20relieved%20to%20have%20a%20female%20driver%20and%20tip%20more.%20Still%2C%20she%20acknowledges%20there's%20only%20so%20much%20she%20can%20do.%20Sometimes%2C%20the%20app's%20navigation%20falters%2C%20she%20said%2C%20which%20can%20delay%20some%20rides%20and%20result%20in%20lower%20tips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20some%20days%20when%20I%20don't%20see%20any%20tips%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Cassady%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20drivers%20like%20Jillian%2C%2067%2C%20who%20drives%20in%20Santa%20Clarita%2C%20California%2C%20have%20a%20simple%20solution%20for%20getting%20more%20tips%20%E2%80%94%20asking%20riders%20directly.%20Before%20riders%20get%20out%2C%20she%20asks%20them%20nicely%20if%20they%20could%20leave%20a%20tip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20perfect%20strategy.%20She's%20recently%20gotten%20a%20lot%20of%20%241%20tips%20and%2C%20despite%20keeping%20her%20car%20in%20mint%20condition%2C%20she%20can%20work%20for%20six%20to%20eight%20hours%20without%20a%20tip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2234a91e52-75c7-4807-ae8b-f80865d6bc21%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20inconsistency%20is%20working%20against%20some%20drivers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlex%20Santiago%2C%20a%2048-year-old%20Uber%20driver%20in%20northern%20Virginia%2C%20used%20to%20dress%20business%20casual%20and%20catered%20music%20to%20passengers.%20But%20after%20years%20of%20inconsistent%20tips%2C%20he%20stopped%20trying%20so%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20days%2C%20he%20drives%20with%20slippers%20on.%20Other%20days%2C%20he%20listens%20to%20podcasts%20he%20wants%20to%20hear.%20He%20displays%20signs%20stating%20what%20passengers%20can't%20do%2C%20such%20as%20eating%20or%20talking%20on%20speaker.%20After%20making%20these%20changes%2C%20he%20said%20he%20hasn't%20seen%20tips%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20providing%20amenities%20such%20as%20water%20and%20games%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20run%20a%20day%20care%2C%20I%20drive%20a%20car%2C%26quot%3B%20Santiago%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20realized%20tipping%20patterns%20are%20often%20inconsistent%2C%20even%20though%20he%20still%20aims%20to%20provide%20good%20service%20%E2%80%94%20he%20keeps%20his%20car%20clean%20with%20a%20%2435%20monthly%20subscription%20to%20a%20carwash%2C%20and%20he%20always%20helps%20riders%20with%20luggage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20days%20where%20I'll%20get%20zero%20tips%20on%2020%20rides%2C%20then%20there%20are%20days%20I%20get%20tipped%20eight%20out%20of%2020%20rides%2C%26quot%3B%20Santiago%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJason%20S.%2C%2050%2C%20said%20the%20frequency%20and%20quantity%20of%20tips%20he's%20received%20fell%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20He%20estimates%20between%20a%20third%20to%20half%20of%20riders%20tipped%20pre-pandemic%2C%20but%20now%20he's%20lucky%20if%20it's%20one%20in%20six.%20He%20suspects%20increasing%20rates%20for%20riders%20has%20reduced%20tips%2C%20as%20he%20hasn't%20changed%20his%20driving%20habits.%20Those%20who%20tip%20likely%20always%20tip%20regardless%20of%20service%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20look%20at%20tips%20as%20extra%2C%20now%20I%20desperately%20need%20those%20tips%20to%20keep%20my%20hourly%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Jason%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20be%20able%20to%20earn%20anywhere%20from%20%2432%20an%20hour%20up%20to%20as%20much%20as%20%2455%20an%20hour%20with%20good%20bonuses.%20Now%20if%20I%20hit%20%2425%20an%20hour%2C%20it's%20a%20miracle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20thinks%20there's%20nothing%20he%20can%20do%20differently%20to%20maximize%20tips.%20People%20rarely%20request%20music%20and%20he%20said%20most%20riders%20will%20turn%20down%20candy%20or%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20extra%20good-quality%20ride%20with%20me%20is%20probably%20not%20going%20to%20make%20the%20difference%20to%20a%20person%20who%20doesn't%20want%20to%20tip%20anyway%20to%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20deciding%2C%20'I%20better%20tip%20this%20guy%2C'%26quot%3B%20Jason%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20drivers%2C%20trying%20to%20get%20tips%20can%20backfire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndre%20Kingston%2C%2050%2C%20said%20passengers%20sometimes%20reprimand%20her%20for%20trying%20too%20hard%20to%20get%20tips.%20The%20Detroit-based%20driver%20said%20she'd%20gotten%20one-star%20reviews%20for%20%26quot%3Btalking%20too%20much%26quot%3B%20or%20not%20being%20polite%2C%20even%20though%20she%20says%20she%20always%20greets%20people%20and%20asks%20them%20for%20their%20music%20selection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20talking%20accusations%20that%20hurt%20the%20worst%2C%26quot%3B%20Kingston%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20make%20me%20not%20want%20to%20talk%20to%20others.%20They%20make%20me%20afraid%20to%20open%20my%20mouth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELow%20tipping%20levels%20have%20led%20Jason%2C%20a%2049-year-old%20ride-hailing%20driver%20in%20Phoenix%2C%20to%20no%20longer%20provide%20the%20same%20level%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20open%20doors%20for%20everyone%20and%20adjust%20the%20seats%20for%20everyone%20and%20offer%20whatever%20music%20request%20any%20passenger%20wanted%20and%20engaged%20in%20whatever%20conversation%20the%20passengers%20wanted%20to%20engage%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20don't%20get%20tipped%20for%20it%20anymore%2C%20and%20I'm%20over%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20new%20st