ol%20for%20tech%20workers%20and%20mountaineers%20alike.%20%3Cp%3EMichael%20M.%20Santiago%2F%20Getty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPatagonia%20has%20told%2090%20customer%20service%20staff%20to%20relocate%20to%20one%20of%20seven%20locations%20or%20leave.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20affected%20staff%20have%20three%20days%20to%20inform%20the%20company%20of%20their%20decision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20is%20trying%20to%20improve%20team%20culture%20and%20support%20business%20needs%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESustainable%20outdoors%20brand%20Patagonia%20has%20given%2090%20US%20employees%20a%20choice%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0tell%20the%20company%20you%20are%20willing%20to%20relocate%20by%20Friday%20or%20leave%20your%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20employees%20all%20work%20in%20customer%20services%2C%20known%20at%20Patagonia%20as%20the%20customer%20experience%20(CX)%20team%2C%20and%20are%20able%20to%20work%20remotely%20to%20field%20calls%20and%20inquiries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20first%20alerted%20on%20Tuesday%20morning%20when%20they%20received%20a%20text%20and%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%2010%20a.m.%20PST%20we%20will%20be%20hosting%20an%20important%20Town%20Hall%20Meeting%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20internal%20email%2C%20which%20was%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20understand%20that%20some%20are%20scheduled%20to%20be%20off%20today%2C%20but%20please%20know%20that%20we%20will%20pay%20you%20for%20the%20day%20%5B8%20hours%5D%20if%20you%20can%20make%20the%20time%20to%20attend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHalf%20an%20hour%20later%2C%20in%20a%2015-minute%20town%20hall%20hosted%20by%20executives%20Amy%20Velligan%20and%20Bruce%20Old%2C%20staff%20were%20informed%20that%20the%20team%20would%20be%20moving%20to%20a%20new%20%26quot%3Bhub%26quot%3B%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECX%20employees%20must%20now%20live%20within%2060%20miles%20of%20one%20of%20seven%20%26quot%3Bhubs%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20Atlanta%2C%20Salt%20Lake%20City%2C%20Reno%2C%20Dallas%2C%20Austin%2C%20Chicago%2C%20or%20Pittsburgh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20have%20been%20offered%20%244%2C000%20toward%20relocation%20costs%2C%20and%20extra%20PTO.%20Those%20who%20choose%20to%20relocate%20must%20do%20so%20by%20September%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20not%20willing%20to%20move%20state%2C%20staff%20must%20leave%20the%20company.%20They%20have%20been%20given%2072%20hours%2C%20until%20Friday%2C%20to%20confirm%20their%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20very%20factual.%20If%20you%20don't%20live%20in%20these%20seven%20metro%20areas%2C%20you%20either%20need%20to%20move%20there%20or%20give%20us%20your%20stuff%20and%20hit%20the%20brick%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20affected%20CX%20worker%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20don't%20respond%20by%20Friday%2C%20they%20will%20assume%20that%20we%20have%20chosen%20the%20severance%20package%20and%20we'll%20start%20that%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20town%20hall%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20one-on-one%20meeting%20with%20HR%2C%20before%20access%20to%20company%20laptops%20and%20phones%20was%20shut%20off%20later%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatagonia%20verified%20the%20details%20of%20the%20announcement%20to%20BI%2C%20confirming%20that%2090%20of%20255%20CX%20staff%20in%20the%20US%20were%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Customers%20browsing%20in%20a%20Patagonia%20store.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6138c8b0eedea900193d90c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221336%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20brand%20has%20seven%20stores%20and%20outlets%20in%20California%2C%20but%20the%20state%20was%20not%20chosen%20as%20a%20hub.%20%3Cp%3EGeorge%20Frey%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20definitely%20feel%20like%20I've%20been%20laid%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20CX%20worker%20told%20BI%2C%20asking%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20as%20they%20had%20yet%20to%20finalize%20their%20severance%20package.%20%26quot%3BI've%20never%20been%20late%20for%20work%3B%20I%20have%20gotten%20nothing%20but%20outstanding%20performance%20reviews.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20severance%20package%20was%20generous%2C%20the%20worker%20said%2C%20but%20added%20it%20was%20sad%20to%20see%20a%20company%20they%20had%20believed%20in%20%26quot%3Bfall%20to%20the%20Walmart%20level.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20employees%20BI%20spoke%20to%20said%20they%20were%20accepting%20the%20severance%20and%20did%20not%20know%20anyone%20who%20was%20considering%20relocation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatagonia%20spokesperson%20Corley%20Kenna%20told%20BI%20several%20employees%20had%20already%20indicated%20they%20would%20relocate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20changes%20are%20crucial%20for%20us%20to%20build%20a%20vibrant%20team%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20Kenna%20explained%2C%20adding%20that%20feeling%20disconnected%20had%20been%20a%20common%20complaint%20amongst%20CX%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20hopes%20to%20bring%20staff%20together%20at%20the%20hubs%20at%20least%20once%20every%20six%20weeks%20for%20in-person%20trainings%2C%20company%20gatherings%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpatagonia-hiring-company-culture-add-vs-fit-dean-carter-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EActivism%20Hours%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2245c9b0e5-5466-49a3-ac63-cf358cb994e8%5C%22%3EHub%20locations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPatagonia%20chose%20the%20hubs%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20we%20have%20existing%20community%20and%20retail%20locations%2C%26quot%3B%20Kenna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalifornia%2C%20a%20state%20that%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpatagonia-owner-chouinard-live-car-no-computer-cellphone-clothes-climber-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecore%20to%20the%20brand's%20identity%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20plays%20home%20to%20its%20corporate%20HQ%20in%20Ventura%2C%20as%20well%20as%20seven%20stores%20and%20outlets%2C%20was%20not%20chosen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20employees%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20believed%20this%20was%20because%20Patagonia%20doesn't%20want%20to%20handle%20the%20increased%20demands%20of%20employees%20in%20states%20with%20higher%20costs%20of%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20asking%20for%20raises%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20and%20they%20keep%20telling%20us%20that%20your%20wage%20is%20based%20on%20a%20Reno%20%5Ba%20city%20in%20Nevada%5D%20cost%20of%20living%20and%20where%20you%20choose%20to%20live%20is%20on%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20a%20California-based%20hub%20would%20not%20meet%20the%20criteria%20we%20set%20for%20a%20sustainable%20CX%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20Kenna%20told%20BI%2C%20confirming%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20and%20other%20business%20needs%20contributed%20to%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20is%20that%20our%20CX%20team%20has%20been%20running%20at%20200%25%20to%20300%25%20overstaffed%20for%20much%20of%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Kenna%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20hoped%20to%20reach%20the%20needed%20staffing%20levels%20through%20attrition%2C%20those%20numbers%20were%20very%20low%2C%20and%20retention%20remained%20high.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a8f6fe3-d14b-4002-9135-4ff21acd8992%5C%22%3E'Big%20corp%20in%20sheep's%20clothing'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%2C%20founded%20by%20rock%20climber%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frise-patagonia-yvon-chouinard-history-photos-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYvon%20Chouinard%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%201973%2C%20was%20ranked%20the%20most%20reputable%20brand%20in%20the%20US%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2023%2F05%2F23%2Fcorporate-brands-reputation-america%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_bla