b0bbb2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fck77gg8219do%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20socialite%20says%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bforce-fed%20medications%20and%20sexually%20abused%20by%20staff%26quot%3B%20while%20at%20a%20care%20facility%20as%20a%20teenager.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fck77gg8219do%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20The%20Big%20Fat%20Indian%20Wedding%20Has%20Become%20Too%20Big%20For%20Comfort%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-09%2Fwedding-cake_620x350_61506340896.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20%24130%20billion%20(Rs%2010.7%20lakh%20crore)%2C%20the%20Indian%20wedding%20industry%20is%20second%20only%20to%20the%20food%20and%20grocery%20market%20in%20the%20country.%20A%20recent%20report%20by%20Jefferies%2C%20an%20investment%20firm%2C%20shows%20that%20the%20Indian%20wedding%20market%20is%20twice%20the%20size%20of%20that%20of%20the%20US%20(%2470)%20billion%2C%20and%20only%20a%20tad%20less%20than%20China's%20(%24170%20billion).%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnAn%20average%20Indian%20spends%20about%20%2415%2C000%2C%20or%20Rs%2012%20lakh%2C%20per%20wedding.%20For%20perspective%2C%20that's%20three%20times%20the%20annual%20household%20income%20of%20Rs%204%20lakh%20for%20an%20average%20Indian%20family%2C%20and%20around%20five%20times%20the%20per%20capita%20GDP%20of%20%242%2C900.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20none%20of%20these%20statistics%20is%20as%20ironic%20as%20this%3A%20Indians%20on%20average%20spend%20almost%20twice%20as%20much%20on%20weddings%20than%20on%20education.%20According%20to%20Jeffries%2C%20the%20usual%2018%20years%20of%20education%20in%20India%20come%20up%20to%20only%20around%20Rs%206%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Elite%20Wedding%20Syndrome%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeddings%20are%20an%20important%20part%20of%20Indian%20culture.%20Parents%20start%20saving%20up%20for%20it%20soon%20after%20children%20are%20born%2C%20and%2C%20if%20it's%20a%20girl%20child%2C%20they%20save%20more%20aggressively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarayanan%20Ramaswamy%2C%20Partner%20%26amp%3B%20Head%2C%20Education%20and%20Skill%20Development%20Practice%2C%20KPMG%20in%20India%2C%20says%20about%20the%20Jefferies%20report%3A%20%26quot%3BAggregate%20numbers%20and%20averages%20could%20be%20misleading.%20Indian%20weddings%20are%20much%20more%20than%20a%20mere%20marriage%20of%20two%20individuals.%20It's%20a%20social%20event.%20Hence%20can't%20be%20compared%2C%20as%20a%20category%2C%20with%20western%20wedding%20expenses%20-%20which%20is%20usually%20very%20symbolic.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20few%20uber-opulent%20weddings%20could%20skew%20the%20overall%20wedding%20expenses%20at%20the%20national%20level.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%2C%20wedding%20celebrations%20were%20not%20this%20glamourous%20as%20they%20are%20now%2C%20though%20dowry%20was%20openly%20prevalent%20in%20the%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr%20Channamma%20Kambara%2C%20Assistant%20Professor%2C%20Institute%20for%20Social%20and%20Economic%20Change%2C%20Bengaluru.%20Clothes%2C%20jewellery%2C%20furniture%2C%20expensive%20gifts%2C%20multiple%20grand%20events%20spread%20across%20days%2C%20elaborate%20food%20menus%2C%20and%20mammoth%20guest%20lists%2C%20all%20of%20this%20and%20much%20more%20add%20to%20the%20cost%20of%20weddings%20in%20India.%20Luxury%20weddings%2C%20which%20cost%20around%20Rs%2020-30%20lakh%2C%20involve%20even%20more%20expenditures.%20Understandably%2C%20due%20to%20its%20sheer%20size%20and%20scale%2C%20the%20Indian%20marriage%20market%20is%20an%20important%20growth%20driver%20for%20various%20formal%20and%20informal%20sectors%2C%20including%20apparel%2C%20jewellery%2C%20catering%2C%20travel%2C%20decoration%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20Notably%2C%20wedding%20jewellery%20accounts%20for%2025%25%20of%20the%20total%20expenditure%20in%20a%20wedding%2C%20followed%20by%20catering%20at%2020%25%2C%20and%20events%20at%2015%25.%20As%20for%20those%20who%20prefer%20and%20can%20afford%20'destination'%20weddings%2C%20these%20general%20trends%20have%20no%20limit%20or%20meaning%2F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApart%20from%20Bollywood%2C%20the%20growing%20appeal%20of%20'elite'%20and%20glamorous%20weddings%20has%20become%20a%20cause%20of%20great%20stress%20for%20parents.%20Many%20-%20especially%20brides'%20families%20-%20end%20up%20spending%20way%20beyond%20their%20means%2C%20leading%20to%20high%20indebtedness%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr%20Kambara.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EMarriage%20Over%20Education%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20country's%20rapid%20economic%20growth%20and%20increasing%20prosperity%2C%20education%20still%20remains%20a%20blind%20spot.%20Students%20still%20lack%20access%20to%20quality%20education%2C%20most%20curricula%20are%20outdated%2C%20and%20funding%20is%20less%20than%20adequate.%20India%20spends%20just%20about%203-3.5%25%20of%20its%20GDP%20on%20education.%20The%20US%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20spends%205%25%2C%20while%20Canada%2C%20Japan%20and%20Germany%20respectively%20set%20aside%20around%205.5%25%2C%203.6%25%20and%204.8%25%20of%20their%20GDPs%20for%20education.%20It%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20these%20developed%20nations%20have%20much%20higher%20GDPs%20and%20much%20smaller%20populations%20than%20India's%2C%20for%20which%20experts%20recommend%20an%20education%20budget%20of%20around%206%25%20of%20the%20GDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGirls%20suffer%20the%20most%20in%20this%20sorry%20state%20of%20affairs.%20Gender%20prejudices%20and%20orthodox%20ideas%20continue%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20deterrents%20to%20their%20education%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20poverty%20and%20inadequate%20educational%20opportunities.%20In%20many%20cases%2C%20even%20when%20some%20parents%20have%20been%20willing%20to%20educate%20daughters%2C%20it's%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20getting%20them%20married%20off%20to%20a%20well-paid%20man.%20Thus%2C%20for%20women%20ultimately%2C%20marriage%20remains%20the%20all-governing%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEducation%20is%20something%20one%20expects%20the%20government%20to%20take%20care%20of%2C%20whereas%20weddings%20are%20an%20individual%20expense.%20So%20naturally%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20personal%20expenses%2C%20weddings%20would%20be%20higher%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mr.%20Ramaswamy.%20All%20in%20all%2C%20it's%20great%20news%20that%20the%20wedding%20market%20is%20one%20of%20the%20key%20drivers%20of%20India's%20economy%2C%20but%20there%20has%20to%20be%20equal%20or%20more%20investment%20in%20education%2C%20both%20by%20the%20government%20and%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719480540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-09%2Fwedding-cake_620x350_61506340896.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-big-fat-indian-wedding-has-grown-too-big-for-comfort-5981255%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20average%20Indian%20spends%20about%20%2415%2C000%2C%20or%20Rs%2012%20lakh%2C%20per%20wedding.%20For%20perspective%2C%20that's%20three%20times%20the%20annual%20household%20income%20of%20Rs%204%20lakh%20for%20an%20average%20Indian%20family%2C%20and%20around%20five%20times%20the%20per%20capita%20GDP%20of%20%242%2C900.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-big-