A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111310889%2Cimgsize-68746.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fgolden-days-when-mansoor-ali-khan-pataudi-played-a-prank-on-sharmila-tagore%2Farticleshow%2F111310941.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111310941.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20nostalgic%20recount%2C%20Sharmila%20Tagore%20shared%20her%20first%20meeting%20with%20cricketer%20Mansoor%20Ali%20Khan%20Pataudi%20at%20a%20Kolkata%20cricket%20party.%20Their%20romance%20began%20with%20playful%20phone%20calls%20and%20culminated%20in%20a%2043-year%20marriage.%20Together%2C%20they%20had%20three%20children%2C%20and%20their%20love%20story%20remains%20a%20timeless%20blend%20of%20Bollywood%20and%20cricket%20history.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fgolden-days-when-mansoor-ali-khan-pataudi-played-a-prank-on-sharmila-tagore%2Farticleshow%2F111310941.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Every%20Indian%20Over%20Age%20Of%2070%20To%20Get%20Free%20Healthcare%20Under%20Government%20Scheme%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20Indian%20citizens%20aged%20above%2070%20years%20will%20be%20provided%20free%20treatment%20under%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20health%20insurance%20scheme%2C%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opening%20of%2025%2C000%20Jan%20Aushadhi%20Kendras%20in%20the%20country%20is%20also%20progressing%20at%20a%20fast%20pace%2C%20she%20said%20while%20addressing%20the%20joint%20sitting%20of%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat-Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana%20(AB-PMJAY)%2C%20free%20health%20services%20are%20being%20provided%20to%2055%20crore%20beneficiaries%2C%20President%20Murmu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurther%2C%20the%20Government%20is%20going%20to%20take%20yet%20another%20decision%20in%20this%20area.%20Now%20every%20elderly%20person%20above%2070%20years%20of%20age%20will%20also%20be%20covered%20and%20get%20the%20benefit%20of%20free%20treatment%20under%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Yojana%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20President%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AB-PMJAY%2C%20the%20largest%20publicly%20funded%20health%20insurance%20scheme%20in%20the%20world%2C%20aims%20to%20provide%20health%20cover%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20per%20family%20per%20year%20for%20secondary%20and%20tertiary%20care%20hospitalisation%20to%2012%20crore%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHospital%20Empanelment%20and%20Management%20(HEM)%20guidelines%20for%20empanelment%20of%20hospitals%20under%20AB-PMJAY%20mandates%20the%20State%20Health%20Agencies%20(SHAs)%20with%20the%20responsibility%20of%20empanelling%20hospitals%20under%20the%20scheme.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719479880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-01%2Fqrkq57t_coronavirus-india-generic-hospital-generic-covid-hospital-reuters-650_625x300_10_January_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fevery-indian-citizen-over-age-of-70-to-get-free-healthcare-under-governments-ayushman-bharat-scheme-5980273%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Every%20Indian%20citizens%20aged%20above%2070%20years%20will%20be%20provided%20free%20treatment%20under%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20health%20insurance%20scheme%2C%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fevery-indian-citizen-over-age-o