a.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-06%2F27%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1719478486-5586.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Fgadgets%2Fvivo-t3-lite-budget-5g-smartphone-with-50mp-ai-camera-launched-in-india-124062700549_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Vivo%20T3%20Lite%205G%20will%20be%20available%20for%20purchase%20from%20July%204%20on%20the%20company's%20official%20India%20website%2C%20e-commerce%20platform%20Flipkart%2C%20and%20at%20select%20retail%20stores%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Fgadgets%2Fvivo-t3-lite-budget-5g-smartphone-with-50mp-ai-camera-launched-in-india-124062700549_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Fgadgets%2Fvivo-t3-lite-budget-5g-smartphone-with-50mp-ai-camera-launched-in-india-124062700549_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Fgadgets%2Fvivo-t3-lite-budget-5g-smartphone-with-50mp-ai-camera-launched-in-india-124062700549_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opposition's%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Face%3F%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20Replies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20alliance%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%2C%20Congress%20and%20NCP%20(Sharad%20Pawar%20faction)%20will%20reveal%20its%20Chief%20Minister%20choice%20for%20Maharashtra%20in%20due%20course%2C%20but%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%20must%20show%20the%20%26quot%3Bface%20of%20failure%26quot%3B%20first%2C%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interaction%20with%20the%20media%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20was%20asked%20if%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20had%20reached%20an%20agreement%20on%20a%20Chief%20Minister%20candidate%20for%20Maharashtra%2C%20where%20Assembly%20polls%20are%20due%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20polls%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20tight%20contest%20after%20the%20MVA%20trumped%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20of%20BJP%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Eknath%20Shinde)%20and%20NCP%20(Ajit%20Pawar)%20in%20this%20general%20election.%20Out%20of%20the%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20the%20MVA%20won%2030%20and%20the%20NDA%20bloc%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Monsoon%20Session%20of%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20started%20today%20and%20top%20leaders%20of%20the%20government%20and%20Opposition%20were%20at%20the%20House.%20Former%20Chief%20Minister%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20the%20BJP's%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20now%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20shared%20an%20awkward%20moment%20while%20they%20were%20waiting%20for%20the%20lift%20at%20the%20Assembly%20building.%20A%20video%20that%20has%20now%20circulated%20on%20social%20media%20shows%20the%20two%20leaders%20exchanging%20words%20as%20they%20wait%20for%20the%20lift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20light-hearted%20interaction%2C%20pictures%20of%20which%20have%20emerged%2C%20was%20between%20BJP%20minister%20Chandrakant%20Patil%20and%20Mr%20Thackeray.%20When%20the%20BJP%20leader%20gave%20a%20bar%20of%20chocolate%20to%20Mr%20Thackeray%2C%20he%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BTomorrow%20you%20will%20give%20chocolate%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Maharashtra.%26quot%3B%20The%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20was%20clearly%20referring%20to%20the%20state%20budget%20that%20is%20likely%20to%20offer%20sops%20to%20woo%20voters%20ahead%20of%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20chat%20with%20the%20media%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20targeted%20the%20central%20government%20over%20the%20huge%20issue%20surrounding%20irregularities%20in%20the%20National%20Eligibility%20cum%20Entrance%20Test%20for%20medical%20education%20aspirants.%20He%20also%20referred%20to%20reports%20of%20rainwater%20leaking%20into%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20--%20these%20reports%20have%20been%20trashed%20by%20the%20temple%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20leakage%20government%20in%20Delhi%20and%20here.%20It%20happened%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20here%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20Maharashtra%20and%20central%20governments%20over%20paper%20leaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountering%20Mr%20Fadnavis'%20charge%20that%20question%20papers%20of%20more%20competitive%20exams%20leaked%20during%20Mr%20Thackeray's%20tenure%2C%20he%20replied%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20one%20of%20their%20fake%20narratives.%20Most%20of%20our%20exams%20happened%20during%20Covid-19%2C%20most%20exams%20were%20online%2C%20whenever%20issues%20happened%20we%20re-conducted%20exams%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20upcoming%20Maharashtra%20election%20is%20extremely%20significant%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20splits%20in%20two%20key%20political%20forces%20in%20the%20state%20over%20the%20past%20two%20years.%20In%20the%20last%20state%20election%20in%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20undivided%20Shiv%20Sena%20fought%20in%20alliance%20and%20secured%20a%20majority.%20But%20the%20allies%20fell%20through%20over%20rotational%20chiefministership%20and%20Mr%20Thackeray%20tied%20up%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20to%20form%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20however%2C%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20government%20was%20topped%20after%20his%20trusted%20lieutenant%20Eknath%20Shinde%20led%20a%20mutiny%20that%20split%20the%20Shiv%20Sena.%20Mr%20Shinde%20tied%20up%20with%20the%20BJP%20to%20form%20the%20next%20government.%20Subsequently%2C%20NCP%20leader%20Ajit%20Pawar%20rebelled%20against%20his%20uncle%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20split%20in%20NCP.%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20too%2C%20joined%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719478920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fqaj9d7m8_uddhav-thackeray-malli