chool%20Crash%20That%20Killed%20Indian-Origin%20Girl%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20UK's%20Crown%20Prosecution%20Service%20(CPS)%20has%20taken%20a%20decision%20not%20to%20charge%20the%20female%20driver%20involved%20in%20a%20freak%20accident%20that%20killed%20an%20Indian-origin%20schoolgirl%20as%20she%20lost%20control%20of%20her%20vehicle%20due%20to%20a%20sudden%20epileptic%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENuria%20Sajjad%20was%20killed%20along%20with%20a%20fellow%20schoolmate%2C%20both%20eight%20years%20old%2C%20when%20a%20Land%20Rover%20crashed%20through%20a%20fence%20at%20their%20Study%20Preparatory%20School%20in%20Wimbledon%2C%20south-west%20London%2C%20last%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaswant%20Narwal%2C%20Chief%20Crown%20Prosecutor%20with%20oversight%20of%20the%20Crown%20Prosecution%20Service%20London%20Homicide%20Unit%2C%20described%20it%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bunthinkable%20tragedy%26quot%3B%20but%20concluded%20on%20Wednesday%20after%20a%20%26quot%3Blengthy%20and%20detailed%20investigation%26quot%3B%20that%20it%20was%20not%20in%20the%20public%20interest%20to%20pursue%20a%20criminal%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20driver%20of%20the%20vehicle%20had%20an%20epileptic%20seizure%20behind%20the%20wheel%2C%20which%20caused%20her%20to%20lose%20control%20of%20the%20vehicle%20which%20then%20drove%20into%20the%20school%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Narwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20evidence%20the%20driver%20had%20ever%20suffered%20a%20similar%20seizure%20before%20and%20she%20had%20no%20previously%20diagnosed%20medical%20condition.%20Because%20there%20is%20nothing%20to%20suggest%20the%20driver%20could%20have%20done%20anything%20to%20predict%20or%20prevent%20this%20tragedy%2C%20it%20is%20not%20in%20the%20public%20interest%20to%20pursue%20a%20criminal%20prosecution%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prosecutor%20said%20that%20in%20reaching%20this%20decision%2C%20the%20CPS%20considered%20the%20driver's%20full%20medical%20reco