nt%20takes%20on%20heightened%20significance%2C%20and%20both%20candidates%20have%20stepped%20up%20their%20personal%20attacks%2C%20with%20national%20polls%20showing%20the%20pair%20neck%20and%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20candidates%20applied%20the%20finishing%20touches%20to%20their%20debate%20strategy%2C%20one%20critical%20question%20remained%3A%20Will%20Trump%20the%20political%20pugilist%20rein%20in%20his%20aggressive%20tendencies%20or%20unleash%20his%20unruliness%2C%20much%20as%20he%20did%20in%20their%20first%20chaotic%20debate%20four%20years%20ago%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20I%20have%20been%20preparing%20for%20it%20for%20my%20whole%20life...%20We'll%20do%20very%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20told%20right-wing%20network%20Newsmax%20in%20an%20interview%20on%20his%20debate%20preparation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20will%20be%20desperate%20to%20avoid%20any%20major%20gaffes.%20He%20meanwhile%20was%20pulling%20no%20punches%20Wednesday%20--%20at%20least%20on%20social%20media%2C%20where%20he%20said%20%26quot%3BDonald%20Trump%20is%20the%20greatest%20threat%20to%20our%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20message%20he%20will%20almost%20certainly%20seek%20to%20hammer%20home%20on%20debate%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20arrives%20Thursday%20on%20Air%20Force%20One%20in%20Atlanta%2C%20capital%20of%20southeastern%20battleground%20Georgia%2C%20for%20the%20duel%20at%20CNN%20headquarters%2C%20while%20his%20challenger%20flies%20in%20on%20his%20private%20jet%2C%20nicknamed%20%26quot%3BTrump%20Force%20One.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20enjoys%20a%20slight%20advantage%20in%20the%20all-important%20swing%20states%20but%20the%20overall%20polling%20looks%20extremely%20close%20in%20an%20election%20likely%20to%20be%20decided%20by%20a%20few%20photo%20finishes%20in%20a%20handful%20of%20battlegrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20Quinnipiac%20University%20poll%20conducted%20Sunday%20shows%20Trump%20edging%20ahead%20of%20Biden%20nationally%