%20polymers%2C%20textiles%2C%20and%20coatings%2C%20creating%20use%20cases%20in%20products%20like%20steel%20bottles%2C%20water%20tanks%2C%20construction%20chemicals%2C%20mattresses%2C%20leather%20upholstery%3B%20even%20the%20automobile%20industry!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20her%20company%2C%20Nanosafe%20Solutions%2C%20has%20created%2040%20products%20using%20their%20active%20copper%20technology.%20They%20also%20closed%20their%20maiden%20funding%20round%20of%20Rs%203.13%20crore%20recently.%20This%20will%20give%20a%20fillip%20to%20their%20mission%20of%20preventing%20imports%20in%20niche%20material%20science%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20India%20Aatmanirbhar%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnasuya%20pursued%20an%20MTech%20in%20Fibre%20Science%20and%20Technology%20from%20IIT-Delhi%2C%20post%20which%20she%20enrolled%20for%20a%20PhD%20program%20in%20the%20same%20institution%20from%202014%20to%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20her%20PhD%20course%20that%20she%20had%20a%20significant%20realisation%20%E2%80%94%20she%20wanted%20to%20make%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353376%2Fabhijeet-gan-rite-water-solutions-million-litres-clean-drinking-water-jal-jeevan-mission-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimpact%20beyond%20academia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20researching%20antimicrobial%20materials%2C%20focusing%20especially%20on%20polymers.%20The%20focus%20of%20my%20doctoral%20research%20was%20developing%20such%20materials.%20While%20we%20worked%20with%20different%20inorganic%20materials%20like%20silver%2C%20copper%2C%20our%20major%20focus%20was%20on%20the%20antimicrobial%20properties%20of%20copper%20nanoparticles%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20scientist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20research%20focused%20on%20developing%20antimicrobial%20materials%20that%20could%20inhibit%20the%20growth%20of%20microorganisms.