rial%20area%20of%20Bawana%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSeeing%20the%20machinery%20helped%20me%20formulate%20the%20venture%20in%20an%20industrially-compatible%20manner.%20Beyond%20my%20work%20at%20the%20lab%2C%20it%20took%20me%20almost%20a%20year%20to%20understand%20the%20process%20on%20ground.%20In%20this%20one%20year%20of%20incubation%2C%20I%20understood%20how%20I%20wanted%20to%20produce%20the%20anti-microbial%20technology%20for%20different%20industries%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%20engineer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20worked%20on%20her%20startup%20baby%2C%20she%20also%20became%20a%20mother.%20By%20March%202020%2C%20she%20had%20all%20the%20processes%20figured%20out%20and%20was%20near-ready%20to%20start%20production.%20And%20what%20set%20the%20ball%20rolling%20were%20the%20antimicrobial%20masks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20the%20technology%3F%20Why%20copper%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENanosafe%E2%80%99s%20patented%20technology%20is%20based%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352011%2Fnikhil-kumar-chintan-prajapati-greenevo-bio-bottles-plastic-free-sugarcane-biodegradable%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eactive%20copper%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20protects%20against%20the%20different%20microbes%20like%20bacteria%2C%20virus%2C%20fungi%20and%20algae%20in%20the%20environment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-36-1719410198.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Anasuya%20Roy%20launched%20Nanosafe%20Solutions%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-36-1719410198.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-36-1719410198-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-36-1719410198-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-36-1719410198-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-36-1719410198-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354462%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Anasuya%20Roy%20launched%20Nanosafe%20Solutions%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20micronutrient%20and%20has%20antimicrobial%20properties.%20This%20makes%20our%20technology%20safe%20and%20sustainable%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20scientist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECopper%20in%20India%20is%20generally%20used%20for%20disinfection%20because%20of%20its%20%E2%80%98purifying%E2%80%99%20properties%20as%20per%20traditional%20sciences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20developed%20technology%20which%20stems%20from%20the%20traditional%20science%20that%20advocates%20the%20use%20of%20copper%20for%20the%20purification%20of%20water.%20We%20have%20synthesised%20it%20to%20act%20against%20four%20different%20microbes%20%E2%80%94%20bacteria%2C%20virus%2C%20fungi%20and%20algae.%20While%20most%20companies%20act%20only%20against%20one%20of%20the%20four%2C%20we%20are%20the%20only%20ones%20working%20against%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Anasuya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20has%20four%20patents%20for%20the%20usage%20of%20active%20copper%20in%20different%20ways.%20The%20founder%20also%20shares%20that%20what%20makes%20the%20technology%20unique%20is%20copper%2C%20the%20core%20ingredient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20technologies%20based%20on%20silver.%20While%20nano%20silver%20is%20toxic%20for%20human%20consumption%2C%20copper%20is%20safe%20on%20all%20these%20parameters%3B%20is%20sustainable%20and%20is%20also%20an%20essential%20micronutrient%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20put%20it%20simply%2C%20the%20technology%20harnesses%20the%20power%20of%20active%20copper%20to%20disinfect%20the%20product%20from%20microbes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENanosafe%E2%80%99s%20patented%20process%20synthesises%20source%20copper%20into%20active%20micro-size%20particles%2C%20which%20is%20then%20used%20to%20create%20formulations%20in%20powder%2C%20liquid%20and%20other%20forms%2C%20which%20then%20kill%20the%20microbes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20particles%20are%20then%20combined%20with%20other%20materials%20to%20produce%20commercially-viable%20products.%20These%20products%20are%20used%20across%20different%20materials%20like%20plastic%2C%20foam%2C%20textiles%2C%20polymers%2C%20paints%2C%20coatings%20and%20cosmetics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20of%20our%20formulations%20are%20substantiated%20across%20different%20ISO%20(International%20Organisation%20for%20Standardisation)%20and%20ASTM%20(American%20Society%20for%20Testing%20and%20Materials)%20testing%20standards%20with%20consistent%2099.99%25%20antimicrobial%20activity%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOff%20the%20beaten%20track%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20selling%20masks%2C%20she%20was%20introduced%20to%20her%20co-founder%20Nirav%20Mehta%2C%20who%20suggested%C2%A0%20pivoting%20to%20other%20industries.%20They%20diversified%20to%20plastic%2C%20polymer%20materials%2C%20starting%20with%20water%20tanks%20and%20pipes%2C%20which%20are%20prone%20to%20microbial%20infections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20water%20segment%2C%20they%20moved%20to%20foam%20used%20in%20mattresses%2C%20where%20there%20was%20a%20clear%20need%20for%20disinfection.%20They%20are%20now%20also%20working%20with%20automobile%20companies%20to%20make%20the%20frequent%20touch%20points%20inside%20antimicrobial.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20customers%20include%20Astral%20Pipes%2C%20Supreme%2C%20LG%20and%20more.%20The%20scientist%20adds%20that%20they%20customise%20the%20technology%20based%20on%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20customer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENanosafe%20has%20won%20several%20awards%20for%20its%20pioneering%20technology%20including%20the%20National%20Start%20Up%20Award%202023%20and%20the%20National%20Technology%20Excellence%20Award%202022%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20ahead%2C%20Anasuya%20wants%20Nanosafe%20to%20become%20a%20powerhouse%20in%20the%20material%20science%E2%80%99s%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20working%20on%20building%20other%20niche%20technologies%20to%20champion%20the%20cause%20of%20import%20substitution%20and%20export%20promotion%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%3A%20Dr%20Anasuya%20Roy%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719411948000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-26-at-16.42.54-1719410205.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D354461%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Putting%20her%20PhD%20thesis%20to%20practical%20use%2C%20Dr%20Anasuya%20Roy%20launched%20Nanosafe%20Solutions.%20Her%20company%20uses%20a%20patented%20antimicrobial%20active%20copper%20technology%20to%20disinfect%20everything%20from%20water%20bottles%20and%20cosmetics%20to%20textiles%20and%20polymers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354461%2Fanti-microbial-water-bottles-tanks-mattresses-anasuya-roy-iit-delhi-phd-active-copper-technology%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Monsoon%2C%20%23DonateARoof%20To%20Help%20200%20Underprivileged%20Kids%20Study%20in%20Safety%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20few%20years%20from%20now%2C%20you%20will%20spot%20a%2