to%20work%20with%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbio-pen-2-1719320147.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20pen%20is%20made%20with%20bamboo%2C%20coconut%20shell%20and%20non%20toxic%20ink%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbio-pen-2-1719320147.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbio-pen-2-1719320147-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbio-pen-2-1719320147-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbio-pen-2-1719320147-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbio-pen-2-1719320147-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354251%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20pen%20is%20made%20with%20bamboo%2C%20coconut%20shell%20and%20non-toxic%20ink.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20industry%20was%20already%20shifting%20towards%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F278549%2Feco-friendly-biodegradable-disposable-tableware-cutlery-party-buy-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euse-and-throw%20disposable%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20design%20and%20virtue.%20The%20entire%20industry%20embraced%20this%20disposable%20mindset.%20When%20I%20joined%20in%202016%2C%20it%20took%20me%20just%20a%20few%20months%2C%20or%20at%20most%20a%20year%2C%20to%20realise%20that%20this%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20something%20I%20could%20devote%20the%20next%2010%20or%2020%20years%20to.%20Given%20my%20commitment%20to%20environmental%20sustainability%2C%20I%20